<odoo>
    <data>
        

        

        <!-- action -->
        <record :id="action.id" model="ir.actions.act_window">
            <field name="name">{{action.name}}</field>
            <field name="domain">{{action.domain}}</field>
            <field name="context">{{action.context}}</field>
            <field name="res_model">{{model._modelName}}</field>
            <field name="view_mode">{{action.view_mode}}</field>
            <field name="view_ids" :eval="[(5, 0, 0),
           (0, 0, {'view_mode': 'tree', 'view_id': ref('delivery_container_tree')}),
           (0, 0, {'view_mode': 'form', 'view_id': ref('delivery_container_form')}),
    ]"/>
            <field name="search_view_id" :ref="search.id"/>
        </record>

        <!-- category -->
        <record id="module_category_delivery_order" model="ir.module.category">
            <field name="name">出运要求权限组</field>
            <field name="description">出运要求模块权限设置(包含出运要求、出运要求明细、合同查询、货柜信息、货柜明细、)</field>
        </record>


        <!-- groups -->
        <record id="group_delivery_order_lock" model="res.groups">
            <field name="name">辅助组-出运要求-只读</field>
            <field name="category_id" ref="module_category_delivery_order"/>
            <field name="implied_ids" eval=""/>
        </record>

        <record id="group_delivery_order_edit" model="res.groups">
            <field name="name">辅助组-出运要求-编辑</field>
            <field name="category_id" ref="module_category_delivery_order"/>
            <field name="implied_ids" eval="[(4,ref('group_delivery_order_lock'))]"/>
        </record>

        <record id="group_delivery_order_admin" model="res.groups">
            <field name="name">辅助组-出运要求-管理员</field>
            <field name="category_id" ref="module_category_delivery_order"/>
            <field name="implied_ids" eval="[(4,ref('group_delivery_order_lock'))]"/>
        </record>

        

    </data>
</odoo>
